logicalColumns.name: Pending Auto Create Days (OU WD)
logicalColumns.description:
Calculates the working days between PR approved date, as it appears in header table and current date time.
WD calculation is based on the country of OU from the PR line. if 81 - IL calc else - ROW calc

logicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE  WHEN %1 = 'Y' THEN  CASE  WHEN %2 = 81 THEN  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) - %3 - 2 *  FLOOR(( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) - %3) / 7) +  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) -  DAYOFWEEK(%3) < 0 THEN  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 7 THEN  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) = 6 THEN -(2) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST ( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) AS DATE ) + 1 -  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) ELSE -(1) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 6 THEN -(2) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) ELSE -(2) END  END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) -  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 0 THEN  CASE  WHEN  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) -  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM %3) < 0 THEN  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) IN (6, 7) THEN -(2) - 1 + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST ( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) AS DATE ) + 1 -  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) ELSE -(2) END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) IN (6, 7) THEN -(1) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST ( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) AS DATE ) + 1 -  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) ELSE 0 END  END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) -  DAYOFWEEK(%3) > 0 AND  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) = 7 THEN -(2) +  CAST ( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) AS DATE ) + 1 -  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) -  DAYOFWEEK(%3) > 0 AND  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) = 6 THEN -(1) +  CAST ( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) AS DATE ) + 1 -  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) ELSE 0 END  END  END  END  ELSE  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) - %3 - 2 *  FLOOR(( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) - %3) / 7) +  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) -  DAYOFWEEK(%3) < 0 THEN  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 7 THEN  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) = 1 THEN -(2) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST ( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) AS DATE ) + 1 -  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) ELSE  CASE  WHEN  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) -  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM %3) >= 0 THEN -(2) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) ELSE -(2) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) END  END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) = 1 THEN -(1) - ( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) -  CAST ( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) AS DATE )) ELSE -(2) END  END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) -  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 0 THEN  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) IN (7, 1) THEN  CASE  WHEN  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) -  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM %3) >= 0 THEN -(1) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST ( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) AS DATE ) + 1 -  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) ELSE -(2) - 1 + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST ( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) AS DATE ) + 1 -  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) -  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM %3) < 0 THEN -(2) ELSE 0 END  END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) -  EXTRACT( HOUR  FROM %3) >= 0 THEN  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) <> 1 AND  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) <> 7 THEN 0 ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 1 AND  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) <> 7 THEN -(1) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 1 AND  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) = 7 THEN -(2) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST ( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) AS DATE ) + 1 -  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) ELSE -(1) +  CAST ( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) AS DATE ) + 1 -  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) END  END  END  ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 1 AND  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) <> 7 THEN -(1) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) = 1 AND  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) = 7 THEN -(2) + %3 -  CAST (%3 AS DATE ) +  CAST ( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) AS DATE ) + 1 -  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) ELSE  CASE  WHEN  DAYOFWEEK(%3) <> 1 AND  DAYOFWEEK( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0)) = 7 THEN -(1) +  CAST ( CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) AS DATE ) + 1 -  CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) ELSE 0 END  END  END  END  END  END  END  ELSE  NULL  END
